9.jpg?1782689506", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/dsk/162/vengeful-possession?utm_source=api", "local": "img/possess/1afb9ce6-658e-40e4-a4a2-9a68182a1e73.jpg"}, {"id": "ab7c0256-eea9-4e0d-932d-c25460eed836", "name": "Possession Engine", "set": "DFT", "set_name": "Aetherdrift", "released": "2025-02-14", "type_line": "Artifact — Vehicle", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/f/2/f206b0a1-50d8-4d53-850d-fb15fd328267.jpg?1782687920", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/f/2/f206b0a1-50d8-4d53-850d-fb15fd328267.jpg?1782687920", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/dft/54/possession-engine?utm_source=api", "local": "img/possess/ab7c0256-eea9-4e0d-932d-c25460eed836.jpg"}, {"id": "7beb7505-b765-486d-a205-78325922a10f", "name": "Edea, Possessed Sorceress", "set": "FIC", "set_name": "Final Fantasy Commander", "released": "2025-12-05", "type_line": "Legendary Creature — Human Warlock", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["B", "R", "U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/6/d/6db60c73-5943-49da-9a8a-f4a382a1c0f0.jpg?1782684340", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/6/d/6db60c73-5943-49da-9a8a-f4a382a1c0f0.jpg?1782684340", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/fic/448/edea-possessed-sorceress?utm_source=api", "local": "img/possess/7beb7505-b765-486d-a205-78325922a10f.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Maritime Guard", "set": "ORI", "html": "To stand as a guardian of the sea, one must <mark>possess</mark> the resolve of a mounting wave.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/0/1008ff1b-7fb0-4570-b23e-9fda14b97640.jpg?1782712647"}, {"card": "Due Respect", "set": "NPH", "html": "&quot;A display of humility is required of those who still <mark>possess</mark> such frailties.&quot;\n—Elesh Norn, Grand Cenobite", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/7/a7159850-964b-4f12-957f-614eb0570544.jpg?1782715188"}, {"card": "Hapless Researcher", "set": "JUD", "html": "Scholars <mark>possess</mark> such lofty knowledge that it shouldn&#x27;t be surprising when they fall.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/2/22ed0ee7-6749-4f38-8e53-c11b46b17e5d.jpg?1782719256"}, {"card": "Crafty Cutpurse", "set": "C21", "html": "<mark>Possession</mark> is eleven-tenths of the pirate code.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/1/117d84f7-45c5-4cfc-a5cd-c44416b48417.jpg?1782705236"}, {"card": "Infernal Captor", "set": "MH3", "html": "<mark>Possession</mark> is nine-tenths of the law. His fist is the other tenth.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/b/6b30243d-511b-47b8-bbed-0395d3de903d.jpg?1782691291"}, {"card": "The Vision and Scarlet Witch", "set": "MSC", "html": "No matter how many times they are disassembled, teleported, or <mark>possessed</mark>, their love always brings them back together.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/3/930afb5f-54b7-4cca-8c28-3e48938f3a43.jpg?1782682061"}, {"card": "Carnivorous Plant", "set": "ME1", "html": "&quot;It had a mouth like that of a great beast, and gnashed its teeth as it strained to reach us. I am thankful it <mark>possessed</mark> no means of locomotion.&quot;\n—Vervamon the Elder", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/f/afa8023b-1afc-4c05-864e-96f65b0aa140.jpg?1782753841"}, {"card": "Virtuous Charge", "set": "PTK", "html": "&quot;The empire belongs to no one man but to all in the empire. He who has virtue shall <mark>possess</mark> it.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/2/72ad4c79-a85d-4fc6-95ab-5a6d6d667579.jpg?1782755049"}, {"card": "Splinter's Technique", "set": "TMT", "html": "&quot;<mark>Possess</mark> the right thinking. Only then can one receive the gifts of strength, knowledge, and peace.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/d/fd3a5465-074a-4688-b79b-68e232076581.jpg?1782683683"}, {"card": "Steal Enchantment", "set": "TMP", "html": "&quot;Why should I flatter another with imitation when I can satisfy myself through <mark>possession</mark>?&quot;\n—Ertai, wizard adept", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/3/734be7fa-0998-4771-9b97-4989b3fc1471.jpg?1782720974"}, {"card": "Extract Power", "set": "MSC", "html": "&quot;Now, it is I who <mark>possess</mark> the Power Cosmic!&quot;\n—Doctor Doom", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/1/11aaa7c6-c79d-48f9-af66-3b360d3b15b5.jpg?1782682645"}, {"card": "Count Nefaria", "set": "MSC", "html": "&quot;If I already <mark>possess</mark> so much, what more could I want? Why, the rest of it, of course!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/6/06fe30ef-75bb-43aa-827c-234dcf57eb6d.jpg?1782682111"}, {"card": "Taste for Mayhem", "set": "RVR", "html": "The taste of blood breaks down what little self-control the Rakdos <mark>possess</mark>.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/3/e3426d58-ff4d-482d-bc78-99b67c55c6d1.jpg?1782731123"}, {"card": "Enigma Drake", "set": "FDN", "html": "Many initiates believe it <mark>possesses</mark> secrets beyond imagining. Many have become meals trying to learn them.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/3/13ce1338-5a46-4d96-a991-d5fa8d4330ae.jpg?1782688694"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Kindly Stranger // Demon-Possessed Witch", "set": "SOI", "html": "Delirium — {2}{B}: Transform this creature. Activate only if there are four or more card types among cards in your graveyard.\nWhen this creature transforms into Demon-<mark>Possessed</mark> Witch, you may destroy target creature."}, {"card": "Unwilling Vessel", "set": "DSK", "html": "Eerie — Whenever an enchantment you control enters and whenever you fully unlock a Room, put a <mark>possession</mark> counter on this creature."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/0/1008ff1b-7fb0-4570-b23e-9fda14b97640.jpg?1782712647", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/0/1008ff1b-7fb0-4570-b23e-9fda14b97640.jpg?1782712647", "card": "Maritime Guard"}}